Insider Activity


Individual




Michael E. Recca



Mr. Michael E. Recca is Chief Financial Officer at Air Industries Group, a Manager at Harvey Acquisition Co. LLC and President & Chief Operating Officer at Sky Capital Holdings Ltd. Mr. Recca was previously employed as President by Granta Capital, Chairman by CellMetrix, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Harvey Electronics, Inc., and a Principal by Taglich Brothers, D'Amadeo, Wagner & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at Sky Capital Enterprises, Inc.



